newest.message:
Contributors for this version * Richard Slater * Tonto Auri
New Features * A troubleshooter will be displayed in the event that an API request times out. * Added link to the EVE Online Stack Exchange Site (Help -> EVE Online Q&A). * Increased default HTTP Timeout from 10 to 20 seconds.
Bugfixes * The setting "Use Advanced Entry Addition" has been renamed to "Set priority when adding skills to plan."
